Description: Stunning 2005 Fender Squier telecaster. This is a 2005 51’ squier telecaster body, which is the most desirable looking telecaster body in my opinion, upgraded with a 2005 Squier telecaster custom neck. The neck is fantastic and rivals some MIM and USA guitars I’ve owned and played. This guitar was really well maintained and is a players guitar with tasteful modifications and upgrades. New strings as well. The guitar originally came with a single coil pickup and Humbucker. This has been replaced with two Alnico 5 lipstick pickups as well as the proper compensated telecaster bridge. There are two holes where the input jack was upgraded and 2 small holes on the back from screws. They are tiny and none of these holes affect the playability in any way and are there only because the guitar was upgraded. I tried to take as detailed photos as possible so you can see. Guitar is in beautiful condition and well maintained for the last 13 years. I’m a strat guy so I’m looking to reinvest this guitar sale into a strat. These stock and factory can sell for more.
Title: 2005 51’ Squier Telecaster With 2005 Squier Tele Custom Neck Modded
